config BATTERY_OZ8806
	tristate "O2Micro OZ8806 fuel gauge (BMT reference, Sunmi V2 shims)"
	depends on I2C
	select POWER_SUPPLY
	help
	  Support for the O2Micro OZ8806 battery management IC used on the
	  Sunmi V2 T5930 POS terminal. This driver is based on the BMT
	  reference design shipped in the MT6755 BSP with Sunmi-side shims
	  to preserve OEM symbol names (typo alias, boot_up_time synonym) and
	  the CV set-point module parameter (sunmi_constant_voltage=8438000).
